Package: spaar
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight toolkit for analysis of tn5-based NGS assays
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author@R: person("Matt", "Lawlor", email = "matt.a.lawlorgmail.com",
                 role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Matt Lawlor <matt.a.lawlor@gmail.com>
Description: Dedicated tools for (very) basic qc and 
    exploratory analysis of tn5-based NGS assays are 
    few and far between. I just want to be able to
    visualize transposase activity and account for 
    insertion bias! And a few more things.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.3),
    magrittr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: GenomicRanges,
    foreach,
    doParallel,
    GenomicAlignments,
    Rsamtools,
    motifmatchr,
    rtracklayer
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
